Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.83,0:00:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.54,0:00:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.52,0:00:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.29,0:00:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.00,0:00:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.77,0:00:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.14,0:00:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.25,0:01:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.96,0:01:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.33,0:01:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.24,0:02:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候到現在\N關於下雨天都沒什麼好回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學入學典禮那天也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.02,0:02:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遠足的時候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.07,0:02:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來\N連初戀的時候也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,要不要一起撐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說,我最喜歡下雨天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我也很喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很合得來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來接你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.98,0:03:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.74,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩千圓還我好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡碰到你真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這樣啊,沒錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你代替我點名\N我就少收你一點,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.32,0:04:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四點開始的語言學喔\N就拜託你囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣\N下雨的日子我總是很倒楣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.34,0:04:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#17 響子的初戀故事\N總是在下雨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該早點出來才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…一起撐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,妳是…七尾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,妳幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的,反正我很閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋,要聊些什麼好呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代在學校嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,應該傍晚就會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他都這麼早就回來啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想看\N星期一和星期三是傍晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期二和星期五是八點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.60,0:05:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期四要打工當家教\N十點才會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期六就不一定了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.47,0:05:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼這麼清楚呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼說呢\N因為我是管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是因為這個緣故嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.12,0:06:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,妳對其他房客的作息\N也掌握得這麼清楚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實也不見得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員真的好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.94,0:06:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接回家不要亂跑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.36,0:06:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一郎,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,把妳的裙子弄髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請到我家清洗一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一留下痕跡就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼麻煩啦,真的沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裙子乾之前\N請妳先穿我的裙子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.26,0:07:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,腰身好緊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我泡茶給妳喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.05,0:07:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話題,話題…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得五代怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.27,0:07:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?妳是指什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.17,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們經常在一起啊\N妳覺得他是個怎麼樣的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很難用一句話來形容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還有其他交往的女生嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.81,0:08:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道耶,好像只有妳一個而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.12,0:08:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是時鐘坡第二中學畢業的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩話題轉得好快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代跟我那時的初戀情人\N長得很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.37,0:08:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初戀情人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我單方面愛慕他而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.38,0:08:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人很有趣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個很棒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.55,0:08:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是跟五代很像會有多棒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.22,0:08:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有男子氣概,而且很帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡像了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他吃營養午餐的時候\N總是最晚吃完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的男朋友很帥耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們第一次見面時\N跟妳在一起的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.64,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,三鷹?\N他只是普通的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有男朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來妳是個寡婦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.71,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我好像問了不該問的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.39,0:09:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,讓我想起他了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.64,0:10:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他也是我的初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(音無老師在外面喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.67,0:11:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們先回去吧,我還有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,每次碰到音無老師的事\N她就像失了魂似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說,又是那個音無老師?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.68,0:12:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,她說要和他一起撐傘回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.32,0:12:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種老頭子有什麼好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.36,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,進來一起撐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.67,0:12:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是三班的同學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,我叫千草響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千草同學\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吧,小心會感冒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳以前做的事還蠻有趣的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我還以為這招很高明呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校的老師啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.54,0:13:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,他只是個兼職的講師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.24,0:13:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟初戀情人結婚對吧\N好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.22,0:13:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看妳高中時代的相簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相簿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也突然覺得很懷念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到五代回來為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.16,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那麼就看到他回來為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.48,0:14:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等雨小一點再回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經有點晚了,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常這個時候已經回來了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.14,0:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的相簿很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空再來玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.88,0:14:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.15,0:15:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候好年輕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是變裝大會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一郎真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎麼現在才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江等到剛剛才走耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.44,0:16:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!她到這裡來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.94,0:16:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,打個電話給她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.94,0:16:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直等到剛剛才走耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫…叫我打電話給她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,為什麼呢?真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.65,0:17:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她又不是那種關係…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.39,0:17:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳誤會了,我才不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊\N我不是那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用打什麼電話啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.33,0:17:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是那種關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,他在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.34,0:17:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,進來進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,小津江嗎?是我,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳今天來找我?\N有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.67,0:17:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,這樣啊,那明天見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上課?我會翹課啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,沒關係,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然說那種話耶,妳很嫉妒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.81,0:18:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰嫉妒啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我掛囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟個笨蛋似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.86,0:18:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.53,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,這把傘還給小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天她忘了帶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我要去上學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.18,0:18:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是今天要翹課\N去跟小津江見面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.58,0:18:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N我跟她又不是那種關係…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事沒什麼好偷偷摸摸的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江會很失望的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.93,0:18:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會破壞\N她的初戀情人的形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可以說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.73,0:19:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼事?\N什麼初戀情人的形象?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.47,0:19:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江說你很像她的初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.51,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼\N原來我不是她的初戀情人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是個很棒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是個很棒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.19,0:19:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要光明正大一點\N這也是為了小津江啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了小津江要光明正大一點?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不了解人家的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,她明明知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.27,0:19:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事\N上次她明明還為了小津江的事吃醋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.15,0:19:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!\N你知道我初戀情人的事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,你有在生氣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要生氣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.42,0:19:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被當作別的男生的替身\N總會不舒服嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.29,0:20:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我也希望\N妳能正視眼前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我有正視你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說\N管理員是個很棒的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.70,0:20:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天她說了她老公的事給我聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨天的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那是她的初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的好專情喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.62,0:20:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼溫文儒雅的響子\N居然會做出這種驚人之舉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定很愛他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.00,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕喔\N可以跟心愛的人結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.11,0:20:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.22,0:21:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你不要死喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳在胡說些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真是痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.42,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種受不了的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.73,0:21:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來一郎\N還活在她的心裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子真是太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對死去的人念念不忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.20,0:21:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡\N為什麼她就不肯多看我一眼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.98,0:22:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.19,0:22:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來一起撐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.33,0:22:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我想一個人走路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.44,0:22:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,感冒了怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.81,0:22:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在鬧什麼彆扭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.15,0:22:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,都不明白人家的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.82,0:22:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,她明明知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.63,0:22:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,總有一天,一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.83,0:22:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.65,0:23:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.69,0:23:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,還是借我撐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看,感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.59,0:23:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間過得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.99,0:23:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來到一刻館\N已經要迎接第二次的聖誕節了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.56,0:23:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,這是我的一點心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.83,0:23:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.57,0:24:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「響子的禮物\N咦!這個要送給我?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.70,0:24:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我用心編織的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.21,0:24:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.00,0:24:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.77,0:24:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.94,0:24:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.82,0:24:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.89,0:25:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.63,0:25:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
